<bibRefCitation author="Ward M" box="[731,882,855,882]" pageId="1" pageNumber="350" pagination="49 - 113" refId="ref6965" refString="Ward M. 1942. Notes on the Crustacea of the Desjardins Museum, Mauritius Institute, with descriptions of new genera and species. Bull Mauritius Inst. 2 (2): 49 - 113." type="journal article" year="1942">Ward, 1942</bibRefCitation>
